text: Nenzingen is a city in the district Konstanz in Baden-Württemberg. Nowerdays Nenzigen has got an population of 3.126 inhabitants (December 2005) ==History== On 21 April 839 Nenzingen was mentioned for the first time as Nancingas in a document of the monastery Reichenau. The place belonged to the county of Nellenburg and came to Austria when the last counts of Nellenburgdied in 1423. Category:Towns in Baden-Württemberg Category:Konstanz (district)
title: Nenzingen
